---
title: Baked Pesto, Onion & Crumbly Cheese Chicken with Wedges & Apple Salad
description: Can you get a more perfectly portioned plate? This nutritionally balanced meal has a healthy serve of chicken
breast coated in the most delectable basil pesto, a crisp apple salad and tasty oven-roast wedges. Delish!
